OL,3,CUnclean utensils and equipment:
OL,4,CRestaurant operator fined for food
OL,5,Chygiene
OL,7,FFood hygiene breaches at two branches
OL,8,Fof an Indian eatery in Reading have
OL,9,Fled to their operator being heavily
OL,10,Ffined.
OL,12,FHungry Budd Ltd, which operates the
OL,13,FBiryani Boyzz restaurants and
OL,14,Ftakeaways in Oxford Road and Wokingham
OL,15,FRoad, was found to have consistently
OL,16,Fpoor food hygiene standards at both
OL,17,Fsites.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
