PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776859866
OL,3,CUnclean utensils and equipment:
OL,4,CRestaurant operator fined for food
OL,5,Chygiene
OL,7,FReading Borough Council said their
OL,8,Fofficers identified a range of serious
OL,9,Ffood safety failures; unclean
OL,10,Fequipment and utensils, lack of food
OL,11,Fsafety controls over safe temperature
OL,12,Ffor food storage, lack of training and
OL,13,Fsupervision of food handlers and
OL,14,Funacceptable food safety management.
OL,16,FCouncil officers carried out
OL,17,Finspections between January and
OL,18,FOctober last year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776859866
OL,3,CUnclean utensils and equipment:
OL,4,CRestaurant operator fined for food
OL,5,Chygiene
OL,7,FThey said that at the Wokingham Road
OL,8,Fsite they found no hot water for 20
OL,9,Fdays and at both premises, food was
OL,10,Ffound to be left well outside safe
OL,11,Ftemperature control.
OL,13,FThere was dirty and broken cooking
OL,14,Fequipment, and generally poor
OL,15,Fcleanliness throughout the premises.
OL,16,FWalls and doors were dirty and there
OL,17,Fwas a tray containing spilt rodent
OL,18,Fbait.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776859866
OL,3,CUnclean utensils and equipment:
OL,4,CRestaurant operator fined for food
OL,5,Chygiene
OL,7,FThey said Hungry Budd Ltd. was given
OL,8,Fmultiple opportunities to make
OL,9,Fimprovements, with support and
OL,10,Fguidance from the Council's Food &
OL,11,FSafety team, but it failed to
OL,12,Fcontinuously uphold improved hygiene
OL,13,Fstandards.
OL,15,FHungry Budd Ltd was fined #12,000 by
OL,16,Fmagistrates in Reading. It was also
OL,17,Fordered to pay a victim surcharge of
OL,18,F#2,000 and prosecution costs of
OL,19,F#5,317.50 to Reading Borough Council.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
