OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776859866
OL,3,CUnclean utensils and equipment:
OL,4,CRestaurant operator fined for food
OL,5,Chygiene
OL,7,FMatthew Golledge, Public Protection
OL,8,FManager at Reading Borough Council
OL,9,Fsaid: "The safety of residents and
OL,10,Fvisitors in Reading is our absolute
OL,11,Fpriority. Food businesses have a legal
OL,12,Fduty to uphold the best hygiene
OL,13,Fstandards, and the public trust them
OL,14,Fto do so.
OL,16,F"However, when an operator repeatedly
OL,17,Ffails to put things right despite
OL,18,Fadvice and support from our officers,
OL,19,Fwe will not hesitate to take
OL,20,Fenforcement action."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
